cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on response generation in conversations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses neural network models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also incorporates attention mechanisms, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses a dataset mined from Reddit comments, which could suggest it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
